properties.areaDesc: Duluth MN to Port Wing WI; Sand Island to Bayfield WI; Port Wing to Sand Island WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 5 at 4:04AM CST until January 5 at 12:00PM CST by NWS Duluth MN
properties.description:
* WHAT...For the Gale Warning, west winds 15 to 25 knots with
gusts up to 40 knots and waves 3 to 6 feet expected. For the
Small Craft Advisory, southwest winds 10 to 20 knots with
gusts up to 25 knots and waves 1 to 4 feet expected.

* WHERE...Duluth MN to Port Wing WI, Port Wing to Sand Island WI
and Sand Island to Bayfield WI.

* WHEN...For the Gale Warning, from noon today to midnight CST
tonight. For the Small Craft Advisory, from 8 AM this morning
to noon CST today.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 8 AM THIS MORNING TO NOON CST TODAY... ...GALE WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM NOON TODAY TO MIDNIGHT CST TONIGHT
